{"tid":219253,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"點解皆大歡喜上神枱但愛回家就收皮","createTime":"2017-04-27T05:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T12:15:13.000Z","uid":38538,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e70b01e5f06352b342401520f56cc7eb0d2549e","tid":219253,"uid":38538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"兩套野都係咁誤會黎誤會去，皆大歡喜最多誤會完之後笑下佢鳩就算，冇後續。過左幾年仲繼續鳩落去剩係呢一份堅持已經夠上神枱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母愛回家雖然情節冇咁鳩，照舊誤黎誤會去，但係次次誤會完之後都會有條撚屌（黎耀祥）出黎講道理，屌你老母我睇電視係想笑下放鬆就算，唔想聽人講經啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鳩嘅境界昇華唔到自然比下去，自然上唔到神枱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申晚晚睇完皆大歡喜先訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35da28d82e7aa0ec02a6c1506e532e5d5d3ddcf4","tid":219253,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"因為時代唔同，仲撚會好似你咁睇TVB嘅人都唔同囉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8257d7437cdd7a44152a25593e189037accc7327","tid":219253,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"十年後就上㗎啦"},{"pid":"efe7fb1d20231e29bf418b809d6e8ffe6a1d0bdc","tid":219253,"uid":103719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"時代係最大原因<br />\n不過你用緊邊套愛回家嚟比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f455928a61175323258010961193b5439415cfe6","tid":219253,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"